metadata.name: #001 – CutePlanet®
metadata.description:
This artwork is the first 3D scene to bring the idea to this Cute Planet collection. Compositing and rendering were done in Cinema 4D, Redshift Render.


🏀 Popular shot on [Dribbble](https://dribbble.com/shots/18890430-The-cute-things-001) by Tran Mau Tri Tam ✪

• Format: PNG.
• Dimension: 4000x4000 px.
• Resolution: 300x300.


🔥 [Official website](https://tranmautritam.com/nfts/001-cuteplanet)
